cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM. 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision, specifically action detection, which suggests that it is likely to be categorized under cs.CV. Additionally, the paper proposes a method for incorporating domain knowledge into the model, which suggests that it may also be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.AI and cs.LG. The use of a tracking module and graph convolutional network also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the sub-categories of cs.RO (robotics) and cs.MM (multimedia).
